latestIgtvVideos.title: BESAN LADDOO RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sharing this three ingredient, TWO STEP no fuss absolutely amazing recipe for besan laddoos! 
it has been my fav since bachpan and that's how we make it in our home, you guys tell me how you do? 
. 
RECIPE:
Ingredients:
4 chamche Ghee
1 bowl besan
a little less than 1 bowl Bura
. 
Step 1: Add ghee to kadhayi, let heat, then add besan and let bhunofy. After it turns golden brown, turn off the flame and let cool. 
 Step 2: After the besan gets cool, add bura to it and mix. Give shape and VIOLA! 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: RANDOM PASTA RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Saucy, cheesy and spicy-sweet! This is THE THANG!!! 
Just one of the things I made with very less ingredients that were lying around the kitchen and the result was so good that I HAD TO TELL YOU ALL ABOUT IT!! 
Hope you guys will try it and will love it as much as I and my family did!!! 
. 
Ingredients:
Sauce:
Tomatoes, diced- 2
Green chilli-  1
Ginger garlic paste
Red chilli powder
Butter
Salt
Sugar

Pasta:
The above mentioned sauce
Pasta
Onions- 2
Capsicum-1 large
Ginger Garlic Paste
Black Pepper
Amchur
Ketchup

Recipe::::
1. Mix all the ingredients mentioned for the sauce and add them as shown in the video. Let them simmer for 5 mins amd you're done! 
2. To the pan add some butter, put in your onions, capsicums, ginger garlic paste and let cook. The add Boiled Pasta. Add a little black pepper and amchur. Mix. 
3. Now add in this some ketchup, the sauce that you just made and lots of cheese ( however much you like) 
Mix, eat and ENJOYYY!!! 
. 
. 
KAHA?! : Ghaaar
KITNE ME?! : A jao
KAISA LAGA?! : BHOT ZYADA TSTAAAYYAYAYAYAUAAUA
. 
. 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: SABUDANA KHICHDI RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Vrat me khayi jane wale meri one of the very fav cheej! 
Papa batate hain ki it is very good for our pet kyunki ye thanda hota hai taseer me. 
Cheekh cheekh k recipe batayi hai, taki tumhe yaad rahe😂
. 
INGREDIENTS:
Sabudana(tapioca pearls) soked in water for atleast 2 hours
Boiled aloo, cubed
Fried Peanuts
Curry Patta
Hari mirchi
Ginger
Jeera
Sendha Namak (pink salt) 

RECIPE:
1. Take a kadhayi, pour in generous amount of ghee. Add in Curry patta, jeera and hari mirchi, also ginger. Sautte nicely. 
2. No add the potato cubes, sautee them too till golden
3. Now add the strained sabudana, namak and peanuts
THAT'S IT!!! 
Hope you guys enjoy this one! 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: MURADABADI DAL RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A bowl full of warm yumza! 
On this happy rainy day, I present to you my mummy's recipe for Muradabadi dal that she learned from our relatives! 
You guys, it's so freaking easy and so SOOOO GOOOD! 
YOU'VE GOT TO TRY IT! 
. 
RECIPE:
Ingredients:
Moong dal- 1 katori
Milk- 3 katori
Jeera, Dhaniya and Laal mirch- Roasted and ground (lal mirch broken into pieces) 
Butter

Kaise banani hai:
1. Take moong dal, soak it into water for 5-6 hours. Then take it out and rinse thoroughly. 
2. Pour 3 katori milk into pressure cooker. Add the dal. Let it come to a boil (to make sure the milk doesn't curdle). When it comes to boil, add salt and close the lid. Let the cooker whistle two times. 
3. Dal is ready! Pour it into bowl, add bhuna pisa jeera, dhaniya and lal mirchi, Nimbu. Top it with generous amount of butter and ENJOY!!!!! 
. 
. 
. 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: CHOCO-FUDGE RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Made with JUST 5 INGREDIENTS! This is going to be your go-to dessert. 
ENJOI! 
*Recipe for the fudge*
Ingredients needed:
1 tin milkmaid 
2tbs Maida
1/2 Cup sugar (ground) 
1/4th Cup Cocoa Powder
100 gms Butter (salted) 

Step 1: Take a kadhayi, Do not turn on flame of gas. Pour in all the  5 ingredients mentioned above together in it.Mix them well. Now turn on the flame and put on sim

Step 2: Keep mixing the maal in kadhayi and don't let it stick. it'll be liquidy first, then will start to bubble up, then it will finally start becoming a little sticky and will start moving together (as shown in the video). At that stage, ADD CHOPPED WALNUTS ( Totally Optional but I LOVE THEM TEXTURE BISHES) 

Step 3: Mix it all up well and let cook for 2 more mins (all the while moving it) Just turn off the flame now.Do not over cook at any cost! Aisa kaida ho jayega  ki daant toot jayenge! Grease any bartan you would want it to take shape in and pour in the fudge. Let cool, cut into cubes after cooling down and enjoy!!! 

Chocolate Fudge is also called 'Sticky jaws'!! They are so fudgy, so chewy so UGH YUMMMMM! You guys have to try this. you'll love it. I promise! Btw I learned the recipe from @milkmaidindia website! And have been using it ever since! 
. 
.
. 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: HANDBEATEN COFFEE RECIPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
No fancy beaters, no fancy equipment, just plain simple handbeaten OG frotheiest coffee ever! 
Video ke beech me maine apne root dialect me baat ki hai 😂 (mai khurja ke pass se hu) 
This is my guilty pleasure!!! 
. 
RECIPE: (for two) 
1. Take a mug, add four tbs cheeni (yes we are meeethe ka cheenta no judgement ok). To this add 1 or 1and1/2 tbs Coffee powder. Mix this well. Then add very little Hot water to it. 

2. Start mixing this with spoon as soon as the water is added. Keep fetofying this till your arm falls apart. ( JK. 5-6 min me ho jayega broooss). Keep beating and you'll see the dark coffee colour will start to change into lighter shade. Do till it look like in the video :p

3. Seperate this frothy maamla into two, add paani and dudh according to your likeness. Mix it well and VIOLA! 
. 
. 
KAHA?! : Ghar bish
KITNE ME?! : ugh
KAISA LAGA?! : THE BEST YAOOOO
. 
. 
.
